 Y

* Term.adt describes the abstract data-type
*  adt-to-java --input boulder.adt --jtom --package adt.boulder --output adt/boulder

* jtom BoulderDashCore.t
* javac *.java
* java BoulderDash2D or appletviewer BoulderDash2d.java

To run the applet needs to find classes for shared-objects, jjTraveler and ATerm-java... The jar file "boulder.jar" shall be used, see BoulderDashNTom.html .


